      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. can u give me a concrete example? like if we had 500k in cogs last year but 25k of that was just shrinkage/lost stuff, and our avg inventory was 100k, how does that change the math compared to if we didn't have the shrinkage? also any ideas on why shrinkage might suddenly spike like that?",
