    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah that makes sense. the security footage didnt show much though, just like small items disappearing from shelves or bins during the night shift. it feels super random, like things are just vanishing into thin air. do you think it could be something systemic, or maybe just some internal stuff happening that we aren't seeing on camera?",
